description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '6 PACK ABS For Beginners You Can Do Anywhere' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: 6 PACK ABS workouts you can do anywhere if you are a beginner. Try these workouts when starting to build ABS!
